    "cWarningAdditions": "",
    "poemName": "The police cause all the chaos",
    "poemAuthor": "Angelos",
    "poemContent": {
        "type": "fragment",
        "styles": [],
        "children": [
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Take out your Formula 1 on the brand-new road,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "And race up the right lane at full speed mode,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Swerve from right to left,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Overtake police cars with utter contempt."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Flashing blue lights,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Pull to the right!"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "There’s been a murderer, A WINK MURDERER! Et-cetera, drugs,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Police chasing cars at 140 miles per hour – thugs,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "For driving how fast, like 80 or 90?"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Kinetic energy and gears – I treasure your velocity but"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Dem tell me, dem tell me, don’t go more than forty"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "But dem chase me at fifty in the pitch-black narrow road."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "And blind me with their azure headlamps."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "It’s a game, a playground game!"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Of cops and robbers,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Or perhaps I’m being hunted by a dodgy imposter!"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "20% gradient and the bloodstream’s infused, with ketones and glucose,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Now, I won’t ever stop."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": ""
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Suddenly a sickly green witch emerges,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "From the gutter at the side or the thorny green hedges."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "It’s not a ghost, IT’S A LIVING MAN!"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "I instinctively clutch the handles of the breaks,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "And slam them till they’ve melted away."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "‘‘Are you crazy, ya menace to society!"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "51mph down a road meant for 40?"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Gimme thirty pounds, you idiot, ya rascal’’"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Avant and quit my sight you man of idiocity!"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "You sped and chased me with heaps of animosity,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Your hand that preys on little innocent victims,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "And steers right over red lights and zebra crossings,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "You are the one who ‘‘verbally abuses’’,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "And your accelerator pedal, constantly misuses."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "You are the menace, you are the idiot,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "You deserve the heaviest fine,"
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 1
            },
            {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Therefore, my hard earned thirty pounds are MINE."
            },
            {
                "type": "newline",
                "count": 2
            }
        ]
    },
    "pageStyle": "poem-centre",
    "pageBackground": ""
}